        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-02-14T18:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-02-14T18:00:00-05:00" n="168" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d168">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">501.BC Indonesia/2–1449: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Consulate General at Batavia</gloss>
                    </hi>
                    <note n="1" xml:id="d168fn1">Repeated as 118 to The Hague and as 78 to New York
                            (<gloss target="#t_USUN1">USUN</gloss>).</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret   us urgent</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <gloss target="#t_niact1">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi>
                        </gloss>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-02-14T18:00:00-05:00">February 14, 1949—6 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>82. <gloss target="#t_Usgoc1">Usgoc</gloss> 291. Neth <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire</hi>
                    <note n="2" xml:id="d168fn2">Not printed.</note> reed today urges postponement
                        <gloss target="#t_UNCFIN1">UNCFI</gloss> Report re establishment interim
                    govt to reasonable later date due to Dutch cabinet crisis and delay Cochran’s
                    arrival Batavia. <gloss target="#t_Dept1">Dept</gloss> considers request
                    reasonable and trusts report can be delayed for brief period. Your comments
                    desired.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
